theorem Topology.dense_of_dense_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (h : closure (interior A) = (Set.univ : Set X)) :
    closure A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  have hsubset : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A :=
    closure_mono interior_subset
  have huniv_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure A := by
    simpa [h] using hsubset
  exact Set.Subset.antisymm (Set.Subset_univ (A := closure A)) huniv_subset

theorem Set.Subset_univ {α : Type*} (A : Set α) : A ⊆ (Set.univ : Set α) := by
  intro x _
  trivial
